{"id": "1421138292509900973", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "973783890110083073", "author_name": "imashino_sukosuko_zamurai", "author_bot": false, "content": "始めて一週間ほど経ったのですが、この中で迎えたほうが良い覚醒体はいますか？", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:16:12.407000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1421138291494883368", "filename": "Screenshot_20250926-231336.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2149542, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1421138291494883368/Screenshot_20250926-231336.png?ex=6a33fdac&is=6a32ac2c&hm=7121eefdb8a98bc32f21b39ecd19e0590e50b27974306c10c786967f542de064&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421139583143378964", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1250088253235789958", "author_name": "mekhane0885", "author_bot": false, "content": "もしルミナスコアに余裕があるのでしたらダフォダイルを確保しておいて損はないと思います。", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:21:20.118000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["973783890110083073"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421138292509900973", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421139750328205372", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1250088253235789958", "author_name": "mekhane0885", "author_bot": false, "content": "他は恒常なのでこれからの新キャラピックアップとかでどうせ出るでしょうし", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:21:59.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421140561179578489", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1250088253235789958", "author_name": "mekhane0885", "author_bot": false, "content": "質問なのですが返魂のコアを使う場合ソレール3凸のために使うのとトゥルー7凸のために使うのではどちらの方が優先度高いでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:25:13.300000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421141794686636043", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "973783890110083073", "author_name": "imashino_sukosuko_zamurai", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます\nここに至るまでかなりのコアを消費しきってるので、なんとか貯蓄して迎えようと思います", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:30:07.391000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1250088253235789958"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421139583143378964", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421142131208356014", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "温存もしくはソレール3", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:31:27.624000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1250088253235789958"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421140561179578489", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421143244347146280", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1250088253235789958", "author_name": "mekhane0885", "author_bot": false, "content": "書いた後に気づいたんですがダフォダイルさんのピックアップは後5日そこらで終わっちゃうのでいっそ一回見送って次の新キャラに向けて貯めておくっていうのもありかもですね", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:35:53.017000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["973783890110083073"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421141794686636043", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421143862830825556", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1250088253235789958", "author_name": "mekhane0885", "author_bot": false, "content": "了解です温存して次のキャラの素体確保にでも使おうと思います", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:38:20.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["797509921343275038"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421142131208356014", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421144363165155348", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルーは好きなら凸っていいと思いますが性能的には無理しなくていいかな。\nソレールの凸は順当に強いので、進めてもいいと思うけどコアは勿体無いから、月のあいてむでいいかと！(次の推しがきて難しくなる問題からは目を背けるとする)", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:40:19.764000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1421144589892583554", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "973783890110083073", "author_name": "imashino_sukosuko_zamurai", "author_bot": false, "content": "必要なら誰かから借りれば済みますし、あと5日で終了なら貯蓄のほうが良さそうですね\nアドバイスありがとうございます", "timestamp": "2025-09-26T14:41:13.820000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1250088253235789958"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1421143244347146280", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
